concentration. } (40. Rdc2! { was nearly winning on the spot! } 40... f5 41. Nxa4 Qxa4 (41... Qb3 42. Nc3 $18 { Knight is getting to -e2 and next hopefully -f4 or -d4. }) 42. Rc3 $18 { after the Bishop is taken, White will group the Rooks either
